Fishing must be done with a Fishing Rod and is an excellent way to catch some fish or other cool items from the sea!

§8§l§nCasting§f§r

Aim at a block of water an press {{ctrl.use}} while holding a fishing rod to cast the lure into the water.

§8§l§nFish On!§f§r

Wait until you start to see a trail of bubbles coming for the lure.

When the bubbles touch the lure, it will bob up and down. Press {{ctrl.use}} to reel in the lure. Be careful not to let your fish get away!